video.title: 2009 VW TOUAREG TDI
video.description: VOLKSWAGEN AND RACING? VOLKSWAGEN AND GREEN VEHICLES? FOR THE GERMAN BRAND THE TWO CONCEPTS ARE COMING TOGETHER IN THEIR TDI PLATFORMS. BUMPER2BUMPERTV LOOKS AT WHAT MAY BE THE SOLUTIONS TO BOTH OF THOSE CHALLENGES IN THE NEWEST VERSION OF A FULL SIZED SUV.
